<plot>This documentary treats movie fans to a behnd-the-scenes look at the making of The Haunting, a remake of the classic horror film about a group of people trapped inside a haunted hosue. Hosted by star Catherine Zeta-Jones, it includes interviews with other members of the cast and crew, who share some of the experiences they had in making the film and discuss some of the special efforts that went into it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?574139</url></doc>
